This paper is about personalized re-ranking in recommender systems, which is a core task in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG). It also involves natural language processing (CL) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, such as the transformer model. Additionally, the proposed model can be applied to various types of recommendation tasks, including e-commerce systems that may involve computer vision (CV) for image-based recommendations. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.CV.
